data.description: Back On The Market.. Time to Sell !!!  PRICE REDUCED.. TIME TO BUY !!! ..New Carpeting Will Be Installed In All Bedrooms Before Closing .... Welcome to this charming property with Amazing Waterview In Front Of Property ... nestled within the esteemed Doral Pointe Community! This well-maintained home has recently received a fresh coat of paint both on its exterior and interior, showcasing a vibrant and inviting appearance that immediately catches the eye.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a space that exudes warmth and comfort. The interior boasts a tasteful blend of ceramic tiles and cozy rugs, creating a perfect balance of style and functionality. The updated look accentuates the property's modern appeal, making it move-in ready for its next fortunate residents. Very Spacious Backyard which is Fenced with Gates on both Sides Of The Property .    This residence is ideally situated, providing convenient access to nearby schools and shopping , ensuring that all essential amenities are within easy reach. Its location within the established Doral Pointe community offers a sense of belonging and security, allowing residents to enjoy a peaceful and well-connected neighborhood.    The motivated listing presents an excellent opportunity for those seeking a property that's not only in great shape but also radiates a sense of pride in ownership. Whether you're looking for a new family home or an investment opportunity, this property ticks all the boxes, promising a comfortable and enjoyable lifestyle.    Don't miss the chance to make this your new home sweet home! With its appealing features, prime location, and motivated listing, this property is ready to welcome its next lucky occupants into a space where convenience, style, and community converge seamlessly.
